com.thomsonreuters.upa.perftools.common

Class DirectoryProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.perftools.common.DirectoryProvider
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IDirectoryProvider, NIDirectoryProvider

    public class DirectoryProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    The directory handler for the upajProvPerf and upajNIProvPerf. Configures a single service and provides encoding and sending of a directory message.
